# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Loupe — .gitignore
# This repo goes PUBLIC. Everything below is either heavy/generated, or the
# owner's PERSONAL working content that must NEVER be published. Review `git
# status` before the first commit; nothing is staged automatically.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── dependencies / build output (regenerated by npm install / vite build) ──
node_modules/
app/node_modules/
app/dist-renderer/
app/dist/
dist/
release/
out/

# ── test + probe artifacts (screenshots, built demo sites, scratch) ──
app/test/artifacts/
**/.dezign-history/
**/.dezign-flow-log.md
**/.dezign-imagery.json
**/.dezign-edits.json
**/.dezign-edits.css
**/.dezign-review.md
**/.dezign-kb/
**/.dezign-flow-engines.json

# ── PERSONAL working content — the owner's real sites + pipeline ledgers (NOT public) ──
baseline/sites/
baseline/_backups/
baseline/pilot-b/
baseline/pilot-c/
baseline/thesis-ab/
thesis-test/
exports/
context/
baseline/PAIN.md
baseline/SITES.md

# ── local agent memory / session state (personal) ──
.claude/
**/.claude/projects/
**/memory/

# ── stray root media + one-off probe scripts (not part of the product) ──
/Untitled design.mp4
/Rectangle 1.png
/grok-image-*.webp
/orbit_cell_tmp.svg
/probe-*.js
/RU-ENG-WEBSITE-TEST

# ── app-local design explorations + accidental screenshots (not shipped) ──
app/design/
app/sample-project/
app/layout-check.png
app/shell-preview.png

# ── secrets / keys / local config (BYOK keys live in userData, never the repo) ──
*.env
.env*
**/dezign-settings.json
**/*secret*
**/*.key
**/*.pem
secrets.*

# ── OS / editor cruft ──
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp

# ── R3 secrets/IP sweep (2026-07-10) — dev scratch + non-redistributable harvested content ──
# scratch probes carry personal absolute paths; sources/ = full-text copies of third-party articles
# (Figma resource library — fine to KEEP on disk for the owner, must not be published or bundled);
# recipes/assets = a third-party site screenshot; system-design-space snippets are marked
# "license: reference/educational" (no redistribution license).
app/test/scratch/
baseline/library/sources/
baseline/library/recipes/assets/
# ── AUDIT-2 F64 — snippet families with no/unclear redistribution rights. This block MUST equal the
# extraResources !snippets/... exclusions in app/package.json (repo/release parity, smoke-asserted).
baseline/library/snippets/system-design-space/
baseline/library/snippets/codrops/
baseline/library/snippets/css-tricks/
baseline/library/snippets/olivierlarose/
baseline/library/snippets/react-bits/
baseline/library/snippets/codepen-picks/

# dev-internal ops note (machine-local restore instructions, attribution superseded by ATTRIBUTION.md)
baseline/VENDOR-MOVED.md

# ── AUDIT-2 F3 (2026-07-11) — kept ON DISK, out of the PUBLIC repo ──
# app/docs = dev-internal audits/handoffs/plans; img-swap = one-off proof with a machine-local path;
# baseline/* non-library scratch = the owner's dev tooling. Only baseline/library ships (F2).
app/docs/
app/test/img-swap.cjs
baseline/.tools/
baseline/snippets/
baseline/skills-lock.json
baseline/README.md
baseline/.gitignore
/app/{}

# root-level dev-internal planning (owner call 2026-07-11: exclude — reversible; README is the public face;
# these carry budget / "unverified thesis" / kill-criteria / backlog, not needed by users or clones)
/CLAUDE.md
/PLAN.md
/DECISIONS.md
/BACKLOG.md
# brand exploration/studies — the PRODUCTION brand assets ship in app/brand/
/brand-loupe/

# Loupe marketing landing site — a separate deliverable (not deployed); owner call 2026-07-14: we push only the
# app + features, not the marketing site. Kept on disk, out of the repo.
/website/
/.website-v2-backup/

# installer-art eyeball previews (BMPs are the real build inputs)
app/build/*.preview.png
app/build/_art-*.html

# WIP README hero/marketing image experiments — not referenced by README yet (it uses media/loupe-app.png);
# the hero is being redone with a real site. Kept on disk, out of the first public push.
media/loupe-hero.png
media/loupe-marketing.png
media/loupe-demo.gif
app/scripts/make-hero.cjs
app/scripts/make-marketing.cjs
